rows.label: qst700107_msg0002
rows.name:
More livestock means
Mother will be pleased!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0004
rows.name:
Sorry to interrupt while
you're all worked up, but
we'll be taking that Armu back.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0006
rows.name:
There's someone waiting
for her to come home.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0007
rows.name: You lie! We found this one first!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0010
rows.name:
What was her name again?
Shishamoo? No, that's not it...

rows.label: qst700107_msg0011
rows.name: Oh, come on, get a grip, Your Highness.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0012
rows.name:
We're looking for Yonma,
Ajijii, and...Iwashisshi...

rows.label: qst700107_msg0013
rows.name:
...Iwashisshi. That's
her, no doubt about it.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0014
rows.name:
I'll give him this, he's
good at taming them.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0016
rows.name:
Sounds delicious! Me
hungry! Getting hungrier!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0018
rows.name:
...This is a problem. I had hoped
to resolve this peacefully.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0019
rows.name:
For those who won't listen
to reason, you have to
*make* them understand.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0020
rows.name:
Can't be helped. Protecting
the Armu is our priority.
